{"word":"κινέω","slug":"κινέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰινέω</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>ϰίω</el> ‘go’]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘cause a change in position’, <b>move <a href='B:470 23:4'>Mt 23:4</a>.</b> W. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐκ\">ἐκ</a></el> in the sense <b>remove <a href='B:730 2:5'>Rv 2:5</a>; <a href='B:730 6:14'>6:14</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘cause to be in motion’, <b>shake,</b> of ridiculing gesture <b><a href='B:470 27:39'>Mt 27:39</a>; incite,</b> of public disturbance <b><a href='B:510 24:5'>Ac 24:5</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sim.\">sim.</a> <b><a href='B:510 21:30'>21:30</a></b> (<el>ἐϰινήϑη ἡ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πόλις\">πόλις</a> ὅλη</el> the whole city was in an uproar)<b>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘be in motion’, <b>move, move around</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b><a href='B:510 17:28'>Ac 17:28</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κίνδυνος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κίνησις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}